		<h2>About Reporting Requirements</h2>
		<p>TVFC requires providers to monitor the temperatures of all refrigerators and freezers containing TVFC vaccine and to submit reports on DSHS forms documenting vaccine inventory and usage.</p>
		<p>All forms are available on the <a title="TVFC publications webpage" href="/immunize/tvfc/publications.aspx#vaccine-inventory">TVFC publications webpage</a>.</p>	
		<p>All records related to the TVFC Program are required to be maintained for five years. These records include (but are not limited to):</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Monthly Biological Report (C-33-A)</li>
			<li>Biological Order Form (C-68)</li>
			<li>Temperature Recording Form (EC-105-xx series)
				<ul>
					<li>Refrigerator Fahrenheit (EC-105-RF)</li>
					<li>Refrigerator Celsius (EC-105-RC)</li>
					<li>Freezer Fahrenheit (EC-105-FF)</li>
					<li>Freezer Celsius (EC-105-FC)</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>Any other reports or required documents</li>
		</ul>
