		<h2>Monthly Requirements</h2>
		<p>On a monthly basis the following documents must be submitted to the DSHS health service region or local health department:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Monthly Biological Report (C-33-A) (only if internet access is unavailable)</li>
			<li>Temperature Recording Form (EC-105-xx)</li>
			<li>Biological Order Form (C-68) (only if internet access is unavailable)</li>
			<li>Any additional/associated forms as required by DSHS health service region or local health department</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Forms may be obtained from the <a title="TVFC Publications page" href="/immunize/tvfc/publications.aspx">TVFC Publications page</a>.</p>
		<p>Monthly online vaccine management is required in the Electronic Vaccine Inventory (EVI) system regardless of whether an order is submitted. Providers without internet access will need to continue to submit the Monthly Biological Report each month to their responsible entity (DSHS health service region or local health department).</p>
